Eve Lister https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eve_Lister 0 Killing Eve is a British-made drama television series produced by Sid Gentle Films for BBC America. It is based on Luke Jennings's Codename Villanelle novella series, and developed for television by Phoebe Waller-Bridge. The first season of eight episodes was ordered on 15 November 2016, and premiered on 8 April 2018. Shortly before its premiere, BBC America renewed Killing Eve for a second season.
